    <time>1768844185</time>
    <user>anag_factory</user>
    <comment>CVE-2026-22029 and CVE-2026-22036 affecting Undici versions (6.21.2, 7.8.0) and @remix-run/router below version 1.23.2 and react-router below version 7.0.0 have been fixed.
Undici has been updated to version 7.18.0, @remix-run/router fixed to latest version 1.23.2, and react-router to version 7.12.0.

This update is to address the security requests from Bugzilla below:

https://bugzilla.suse.com/show_bug.cgi?id=1256475

https://bugzilla.suse.com/show_bug.cgi?id=1256845</comment>
    <requestid>1328107</requestid>
  </revision>
